{
  "graph_id": "g02",
  "description": "G02 Research Graph. Verifies approved claims and finds current literature for a lecture refresh, then freezes a UserApprovedResearchBundle. SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH for the node order — g02_flow.py and the orchestrator skill must agree with this manifest. Authoritative design: docs/02_Architektura_agentow_i_skilli.md. Reviews are runs of ONE physical agent (g02-a10-output-reviewer) with a per-node review_profile; the two user gates are orchestrator steps, not agents. g02_flow.py supports an injectable no-op runner for deterministic wiring tests and a Codex runner for isolated codex exec workers. The current runtime executes sequence serially; discovery nodes marked as a logical fan-out in the design become concurrent only after explicit dependency and scheduler support is added.",
  "orchestrator": "g02-orchestrate-research",
